  "contentHtml": "<figure><a href=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/%24s_!w6Is!,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5de5d442-0449-4f37-a82b-7e09457b3074_2756x748.png\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n<img src=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/%24s_!w6Is!,w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5de5d442-0449-4f37-a82b-7e09457b3074_2756x748.png\" width=\"1456\" height=\"395\" data-size=\"normal\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n\n\n</a></figure>\n<p>In this space on Saturdays, I <a href=\"https://neilpaine.substack.com/t/roundup\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">do a weekly round-up</a> of sorts: Sifting through what I wrote that you might have missed during the week, what I’ve been reading and watching myself, and some other fun things that have been going on.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://neilpaine.substack.com/subscribe?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><span>Subscribe now</span></a></p>\n<hr>\n<h4>📝 What I did this week</h4>\n<p><em>Here are the things I wrote or podcasted about during the previous week, sorted in descending order by quality, popularity and/or current relevance.</em></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>🏀 <strong><a href=\"https://neilpaine.substack.com/p/who-won-the-2026-wnba-offseason\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Who Won the 2026 WNBA Offseason?</a></strong> - With the season tipping off, I analyzed which teams added or subtracted the most projected <a href=\"https://neilpaine.substack.com/i/176608441/2025-26-nba-laker-leaderboard\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">LAKER</a> talent over the fast-paced offseason and what those roster shifts might mean for the championship race. <strong>Related:</strong> </p>\n<ul><li><p><strong><a href=\"https://neilpaine.substack.com/p/2026-wnba-elo-team-power-rankings\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">🏀 2026 WNBA Elo Team Power Rankings and Player Rankings 📈</a><a href=\"https://neilpaine.substack.com/p/2025-26-nba-elo-forecast-and-player\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"> </a></strong>- My <a href=\"https://neilpaine.substack.com/p/2025-wnba-elo-team-power-rankings\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Elo ratings</a> are back and will update throughout the season!</p></li></ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>🏁 <strong><a href=\"https://neilpaine.substack.com/p/alex-zanardi-made-you-believe\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Alex Zanardi Made You Believe</a></strong> - In the days after his death, I wrote my tribute to the late racecar driver, reflecting on the remarkable courage, tenacity and competitive spirit that defined his audacious career.</p>\n<figure><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WuwiqivkKCg&amp;pp=ygUVdGhlIHBhc3MgYWxleCB6YW5hcmRp\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n<img src=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/%24s_!ha-h!,w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd3e48a87-df8d-445b-a5f3-efc3c37026ea_1900x1235.png\" width=\"1456\" height=\"946\" data-size=\"normal\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n\n\n</a><figcaption><strong><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WuwiqivkKCg&amp;pp=ygUVdGhlIHBhc3MgYWxleCB6YW5hcmRp\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">“The Pass”</a></strong></figcaption></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p>🏀 <strong><a href=\"https://neilpaine.substack.com/p/all-signs-point-to-the-knicks-which\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">All Signs Point to the Knicks — Which Is the Problem</a></strong> - With some of the conference’s heavy-hitters<em> (cough, Boston) </em>out of the way, I explored the Knicks’ status as East favorites coming out of Round 1 — and why history suggests that hope is often a dangerous emotion for this franchise.</p></li>\n<li><p>🏒 <strong><a href=\"https://neilpaine.substack.com/p/the-minnesota-wild-took-down-a-colorado\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">The Minnesota Wild Took Down a Colorado Avalanche Dynasty Once Before</a></strong> - I flashed us back to the most iconic win in Wild history, and the massive ripple effects it had on the league, from a Hall of Famer’s retirement to a league-wide lockout.</p></li>\n<li><p>⚾ <strong><a href=\"https://neilpaine.substack.com/p/maybe-the-new-manager-bounce-is-real\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Maybe The New-Manager Bounce Is Real After All</a></strong> - I’ve often suspected that the “bounce” teams get from changing managers is just plain old regression to the mean, but recent data suggests there might be more to the phenomenon.</p></li>\n<li>\n<p>🏁 <strong><a href=\"https://www.nascar.com/news-media/2026/05/07/the-wins-are-nice-but-elliotts-consistency-might-be-his-biggest-title-edge/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">The wins are nice, but Elliott’s consistency might be his biggest title edge</a></strong> - For , I wrote about how Chase Elliott’s ability to avoid “bad days” is proving to be a mathematically superior weapon in the hunt for the Cup title:</p>\n<div class=\"reader-datawrapper\"><a href=\"https://datawrapper.dwcdn.net/tCLIm/2/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/26632b97-81cd-473f-aa8b-41f1c0de6062_1220x1768.png\" alt=\"Nobody has a higher floor than Chase Elliott\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></a><p>Nobody has a higher floor than Chase Elliott</p></div>\n<ul><li><p>🏁🎙️ <strong><a href=\"https://open.spotify.com/episode/0XwWTwC40GWNU3SOjovapX?si=AqUmPCFGQ8KKC8O2YQ5mKA\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Podracing: Chase’s Chase For the Chase</a></strong> - In this week’s episode of , <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/tyler-lauletta-b0399667/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"> Lauletta</a> and I broke down the fast and bumpy pavement in Texas, Elliott’s big win, and whether his consistency is the ultimate championship blueprint. Then we talked betting picks and I paid my tribute to Zanardi in audio form.</p></li></ul>\n</li>\n<li><p>⚾🎧 <strong><a href=\"https://open.spotify.com/episode/3kMy6wTTsdhgtqS78YMBWr?si=_ftaaXAITKy1y_xxDZDeMw\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Garret Anderson with Neil Paine</a></strong> - I joined my friend  to talk about the late Angels OF’s life and surprisingly impactful legacy.</p></li>\n</ul>\n<h4>📊 Chart(s) of the week:</h4>\n<p>Here were my favorite items of the week from <em><strong><a href=\"https://neilpaine.substack.com/p/scoreboard-newsletter-archives\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Scoreboard</a></strong></em>, my daily newsletter for <a href=\"https://sherwood.news/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Sherwood News</a>… </p>\n<p><strong>🏇 </strong><em><strong>On recent Kentucky Derby winners <a href=\"https://neilpaine.substack.com/i/196800481/chart-of-the-day\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">skipping the Preakness</a>…</strong></em></p>\n<div class=\"reader-datawrapper\"><a href=\"https://datawrapper.dwcdn.net/EaU3c/1/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/69a3a057-838c-419d-b6db-13e162233911_1220x1438.png\" alt=\"Recent Derby winners skip the Preakness\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></a><p>Recent Derby winners skip the Preakness</p></div>\n<p><strong>⚾ </strong><em><strong>On college softball’s HR surge…</strong></em></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><strong>🏁 </strong><em><strong>On NASCAR’s <a href=\"https://neilpaine.substack.com/i/196921641/chart-of-the-day\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">most dominant road-racer</a>…</strong></em></p>\n<div class=\"reader-datawrapper\"><a href=\"https://datawrapper.dwcdn.net/TYY4p/1/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/530b27fe-bed9-4c53-a657-ab5666c53484_1220x1256.png\" alt=\"Will it be more SVG, or something different?\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></a><p>Will it be more SVG, or something different?</p></div>\n<p><em>Subscribe to <strong>Scoreboard</strong> by <strong><a href=\"https://join.sherwood.news/scoreboard\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">clicking here</a></strong>!</em></p>\n<h4>👀 Some interesting things I read/watched this week</h4>\n<p><em>A collection of articles (with a heavy focus on my fellow Substackers), videos and other media that I enjoyed and/or found thought-provoking over the past week. I don’t always 100% agree with or endorse what’s linked here… but that’s also sort of the point.</em></p>\n<ul>\n<li><p>🏀 <strong><a href=\"https://www.basketballpoetry.com/p/the-2026-lottery-will-be-cant-miss?utm_source=post-email-title&amp;publication_id=517515&amp;post_id=196802820&amp;utm_campaign=email-post-title&amp;isFreemail=true&amp;r=gwh9&amp;triedRedirect=true&amp;utm_medium=email\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">The 2026 lottery will be can’t-miss television</a> </strong>by  </p></li>\n<li><p>🏀 <strong><a href=\"https://herhoopstats.substack.com/p/can-caitlin-clark-bounce-back-after?utm_source=post-email-title&amp;publication_id=21307&amp;post_id=196954769&amp;utm_campaign=email-post-title&amp;isFreemail=true&amp;r=gwh9&amp;triedRedirect=true&amp;utm_medium=email\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Can Caitlin Clark bounce back after injury, shooting slump?</a></strong> by  </p></li>\n<li><p>🏀 <strong><a href=\"https://baselinewithlinds.substack.com/p/ball-is-lifeand-all-of-its-lessons?utm_source=post-email-title&amp;publication_id=8187944&amp;post_id=195457186&amp;utm_campaign=email-post-title&amp;isFreemail=true&amp;r=gwh9&amp;triedRedirect=true&amp;utm_medium=email\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Ball Is Life...and All of Its Lessons</a></strong> by  </p></li>\n<li><p>🏀 <strong><a href=\"https://highleytj.substack.com/p/modern-day-tanking-is-michael-jordans?utm_source=post-email-title&amp;publication_id=8357897&amp;post_id=196611589&amp;utm_campaign=email-post-title&amp;isFreemail=true&amp;r=gwh9&amp;triedRedirect=true&amp;utm_medium=email\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Modern Day Tanking Is Michael Jordan’s Fault</a> </strong>by  </p></li>\n<li><p>🏀 <strong><a href=\"https://herhoopstats.substack.com/p/how-will-expansion-impact-wnba-roster?utm_source=post-email-title&amp;publication_id=21307&amp;post_id=196572599&amp;utm_campaign=email-post-title&amp;isFreemail=true&amp;r=gwh9&amp;triedRedirect=true&amp;utm_medium=email\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">How will expansion impact WNBA roster building?</a> </strong>by  </p></li>\n<li><p>🏀<strong> <a href=\"https://www.houseofstrauss.com/p/je-suis-tres-fatigue-the-wembanyama?utm_source=post-email-title&amp;publication_id=446127&amp;post_id=196532001&amp;utm_campaign=email-post-title&amp;isFreemail=false&amp;r=gwh9&amp;triedRedirect=true&amp;utm_medium=email\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Je Suis Très Fatigué: The Wembanyama Energy Problem</a> </strong>by  </p></li>\n<li><p>🏀 <strong><a href=\"https://www.readbutterflies.com/p/nba-playoff-defense?utm_source=post-email-title&amp;publication_id=1952068&amp;post_id=196510633&amp;utm_campaign=email-post-title&amp;isFreemail=true&amp;r=gwh9&amp;triedRedirect=true&amp;utm_medium=email\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Cheers to NBA Playoff Defense: Why the playoffs feel so different</a></strong> by  </p></li>\n<li><p>🏀 <strong><a href=\"https://bangnba.substack.com/p/everything-orlando-had-ran-through?utm_source=post-email-title&amp;publication_id=3039167&amp;post_id=196546071&amp;utm_campaign=email-post-title&amp;isFreemail=true&amp;r=gwh9&amp;triedRedirect=true&amp;utm_medium=email\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noope